      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>許せない！
お金のない村から
さらに物を奪おうだなんて！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Unforgivable! How dare they steal even more
from a village that already has no money!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>7</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ったく。
金持ちってのはこれだから</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Geez. That's how rich folks are.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>行こう、リッド！
村のみんなを守らなくちゃ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Let's go, Reid!
We've gotta protect the people of this village!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>7</SpeakerId>
